## Directory Tree (agent-context/)

```
agent-context/
├── AGENT_INDEX.md              <- this file
├── business-context.md         <- product, parent platform, this service's role
├── architecture.md             <- modules, layers, data flow, key abstractions
├── conventions.md              <- naming, DI, logging, transactions
├── api-conventions.md          <- API style + endpoint catalog
├── database.md                 <- schema, migrations, query patterns
├── authentication.md           <- authn flow, authz model
├── error-handling.md           <- exception hierarchy + HTTP status mapping
├── testing.md                  <- test types, framework setup, mocking rules
├── infrastructure.md           <- build, deploy, profiles, observability
├── glossary.md                 <- domain terminology
├── integrations/               <- one file per external system
│   └── {provider}.md           <- e.g., aws.md, kafka.md, stripe.md
└── domains/                    <- one file per bounded context
    └── {context}.md            <- e.g., book-review.md, contracts.md
```

